{"tid":2098272,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚去左良心食店稻香食一蚊乳鴿，到底點賺到錢呀？","createTime":"2020-07-07T11:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T11:30:38.000Z","uid":8968,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"caf4cf1fedcafad4bd8fe4799d003260e2d3b3da","tid":2098272,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iMAP5we.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiMAP5we.jpg&h=dcff5a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩排左4，5個字終於入到去<br />\n坐底即刻叫左個皇牌乳鴿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前一蚊雞都算，乳鴿雖然細隻啲<br />\n但係更加罕有更加珍貴<br />\n屌奶星 竟然都係賣$1？<br />\n<br />\n反正收到正苦1m⋯⋯可以食到1萬隻<br />\n我計過每晚一隻可以食到成27年<br />\n<br />\n慳埋慳埋夠俾首期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n稻香多謝你🙏🏻"},{"pid":"2a334dd5e576a13e6a04f439ee311c7b0ae94788","tid":2098272,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:13:21.000Z","msg":"搞手求打個和同支持藍絲手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cb99a891e47a6c60c19dc1694d83c536a171ec","tid":2098272,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:14:22.000Z","msg":"打個和，你食得開心，佢地就開心"},{"pid":"51a683b843164046cfd99f339950bd40e2352e84","tid":2098272,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02cb99a891e47a6c60c19dc1694d83c536a171ec","tid":2098272,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:14:22.000Z","msg":"打個和，你食得開心，佢地就開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:16:23.000Z","msg":"等緊佢上鴿 好撚期待"},{"pid":"5bc0d65df074459c664b257f8c43be2fac97eeaa","tid":2098272,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"樓主唔驚連衛兵進場屌你？"},{"pid":"3cd53cc1a5af05878181dec2ea87755717403c51","tid":2098272,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T11:17:35.